{"tid":1470033,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"搞記者會向世界宣布香港機場危險,可以輕鬆令機場停用","createTime":"2019-08-14T03:57:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T04:27:49.000Z","uid":267263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a59ce6999fd237036438df1b84f10f0a57e2dbec","tid":1470033,"uid":267263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:57:56.000Z","msg":"我地需要一個<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記者會</span></span></strong>同世界表達香港機場係<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好危險</span></span></strong>依個情況,令旅客<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔使用</span></span></strong>香港機場<br />\n<br />\n我地要攞琴日件事,例如中共派公安混入人群,警察衝入機場打人等,強調香港機場<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">危及</span></span></strong>到步旅客安全<br />\n<br />\n同時,我地要將612,721,811成為我地抗爭主要理據(播片)<br />\n<br />\n最重要一點,我地要對世界宣佈香港機場行動<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不排除升級</span></span></strong>(我地唔一定要真係升級),唔需要講明幾時升同點樣升。最重要係依個消息一出,外國旅客/政府自然因為怕有危險<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">取消</span></span></strong>航班唔嚟香港機場。<br />\n<br />\n我地要表明機場可能發生<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">嚴重警民衝突</span></strong></span>(播埋黑警係室內放催淚彈),<br />\n呼龥航空公司唔好淨係注重賺錢而不顧旅客安全強行飛嚟香港。<br />\n<br />\n依個消息一出,香港機場自然<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">收皮</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n記者會建議係機場著full gear 搞,令人相信香港機場將發生嚴重警民衝突<br />\n<br />\n記者會用唔同語言(英文最重要)<br />\n<br />\n重申:雖然我地<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔一定</span></span></strong>要真係升級,最重要係依個消息一出,外國旅客/政府自然因為有<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">危險意識</span></span></strong>取消航班唔嚟香港機場。<br />\n機場係政府<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">春袋</span></span></strong>,停一日商家就蝕幾千萬,佢冇可能死頂落去<br />\n<br />\n推比更多人知"},{"pid":"e70931eb4cd645a73fd16b1c03b6d0d649445956","tid":1470033,"uid":267263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:58:26.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"af51e362a210f3a9c559a62dc6cee430e8514611","tid":1470033,"uid":267263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:58:41.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"bc644dce160286eab33c78ce5cb25ab1ba6f48ee","tid":1470033,"uid":267263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:58:52.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"71bfadb0c6e486ddbe408cb77744c900113e5e3b","tid":1470033,"uid":267263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:59:02.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"a2eb3ecc54d272ae3576ed1526e4a9be28318cc2","tid":1470033,"uid":267263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:59:14.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"05d6797c753e98538ec013d12615b5a11994ac49","tid":1470033,"uid":267263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:59:33.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"07a9597d51c60da8186721a3a5cfa2e0309b2cf6","tid":1470033,"uid":267263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:00:16.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"a164f77b28b47a19c70ec26b960870f668fc0ab3","tid":1470033,"uid":267263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:00:28.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"291882c273d808226e4ea0d4438977d61004479f","tid":1470033,"uid":267263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:00:48.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"0d7db2fb13c2cfbf1ca3a0127a6f1fc5c6a214dc","tid":1470033,"uid":267263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:01:03.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"36d0b39ccd122df9f607de8d36f0cd487609ca6c","tid":1470033,"uid":267263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:01:13.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"fe37758efbfe80235718c9df1306c5ed81a9bc42","tid":1470033,"uid":267263,"like":0,"dislike"